ğŸ‘‰ Cache churn â€“ a lot of the data will never be read

ğğğ¬ğ­ ğ©ğ«ğšğœğ­ğ¢ğœğ ğ„ğ¥ğšğ¬ğ­ğ¢ğ‚ğšğœğ¡ğ:
ğŸ‘‰ Lazy Loading / Cache aside is easy to implement and works for many situations as a foundation, especially on the read side
