ğŸ‘‰ It is free but you pay for the underlying instances.
ğŸ‘‰ Deployment- All at once, Rolling, Rolling with additional batches, Blue Green, Traffic Splitting.
ğŸ‘‰ CLI- eb create, eb status, eb health, eb events, eb logs, eb open, eb deploy, eb config, eb terminate.
ğŸ‘‰ Lifecycle Policy- to phase out old application versions.
